  <div class="wrongBookBody">
    <h2>See a Problem?</h2>
    <div class="wrongBookText">
      <div class="description">
        We’d love your help.
        Let us know what’s wrong with this preview of
          <cite>In the Company of Cheerful Ladies</cite> by Alexander McCall Smith.
      </div>
