<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1112898-who-is-or-where-did-the-case-about-the">Who is or where did the case about the missing Zambian financier come from, I finished the book but don&#39;t remember how or when this case gets started. Is it a carryover from a previous book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1112898'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F7053.In_the_Company_of_Cheerful_Ladies">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1112898-who-is-or-where-did-the-case-about-the">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1112898-who-is-or-where-did-the-case-about-the">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11474112-sheena"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1582198917i/11474112._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11474112-sheena">Sheena</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No it is not a carryover because I am reading the books in sequence. The Zambian absconding financier case was a special request from a firm of lawyer<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No it is not a carryover because I am reading the books in sequence. The Zambian absconding financier case was a special request from a firm of lawyers in Zambia, who were looking for the runaway businessman who apparently had decamped with a lot of their client's money. The No. 1 Ladies Detective Agency 's reputation has spread beyond the borders of Botswana, and it is being approached by foreign clients.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
