<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/508385-i-ve-just-read-it-but-i-don-t-understand">I&#39;ve just read it but I don&#39;t understand the relation between the name of the book and the book itself. Who are those cheerful ladies? Who is in their company?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_508385'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F7053.In_the_Company_of_Cheerful_Ladies">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/508385-i-ve-just-read-it-but-i-don-t-understand">6 years ago</a>
